<lb ed="F" n="0118a16"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead>大王觀世音經一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="F" n="0118a17"/><cb:div><p xml:id="pF01p0118a1701"><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>佛</corr><sic><unclear/></sic></choice>說觀世音<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>經一卷</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>讀誦</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>千遍得度苦難拔除生死罪觀世音菩薩南无佛佛國有緣佛法相因
<lb ed="F" n="0118a18"/><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>常樂</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>我<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>淨</corr><sic><unclear/></sic></choice>　<unclear/><unclear/><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>南无摩訶波若</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>是大神呪　南无摩訶波若是大明呪　南无摩訶波若是大
<lb ed="F" n="0118a19"/><unclear/>等等呪　<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>淨光祕密佛</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>　<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>法藏</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>佛　師子吼神足遊王佛　告須弥登王佛　法護佛　金剛
<lb ed="F" n="0118a20"/><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>藏師</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>子游戲佛　藥師瑠璃<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>光</corr><sic><unclear/></sic></choice>佛　普光功德山王佛　善住功德寶王佛　六方六佛名号　東
<lb ed="F" n="0118a21"/>方寶光月<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>殿</corr><sic><unclear/></sic></choice>妙尊音王佛　南方樹根華王佛　西方<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>皂</corr><sic><unclear/></sic></choice>王神通<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>焰</corr><sic>艶</sic></choice>華王佛　北方月殿清淨佛
<lb ed="F" n="0118a22"/>　上方无數精進寶首佛　下方善寂月音王佛　釋迦牟𡰱佛　弥勒佛　中央一切眾生在此
<lb ed="F" n="0118a23"/><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>世</corr><sic><unclear/></sic></choice>界中者行住於地上及<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>在虛空中慈憂</corr><sic><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/></sic></choice>於一切令各安休息晝夜脩治心常應誦此經消伏於</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>